<fieldset>Author: detamic
Map name: de_western_story.bsp
email: detamic@wanadoo.fr


This is a counter strike source map. You can play up to 32 players. 

Instructions:
Extract the de_western_story.bsp and .nav files into the maps folder in the game dir.

Description:
The scene take place during west conquest, in a little town of far west. Terrorists have escaped from jail and want to take their revenge. So they want to attack Bank (A bomb site) or Mayor house (B bomb site), whereas counters have been employed to guard it...
Terrorist can use train, which can be started by pressing button of engine. 
TIPS: B site can be easily reach by train... 

Have fun!
